Hosted by Chris Mooney and Indre Viskontas, each episode takes on a specific issue and features lively discussion with leading scientists, researchers and writers.

Point of Inquiry is produced by Adam Isaak at the Center for Inquiry in Amherst, N.Y.]]></description>
