            <link><![CDATA[http://pointofinquiry.libsyn.com/greta-christina-why-are-you-atheists-so-angry]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>Our guest this week is Greta Christina, a leading atheist blogger, speaker, and commentator, and a regular contributor to&nbsp;<a href="http://www.alternet.org/authors/8504/">AlterNet.org</a>.</p>
<p>Christina is author of the new ebook <em>Why Are You Atheists So Angry?: 99 Things that Piss Off the Godless</em>, which grows out of a&nbsp;<a href="http://gretachristina.typepad.com/greta_christinas_weblog/2007/10/atheists-and-an.html">2007 blog post</a>&nbsp;on the same topic. The book will also be out in print in June.</p>
<p><strong>Greta Christina</strong> blogs at&nbsp;<a href="http://freethoughtblogs.com/greta/">FreeThoughtBlogs.com</a>, and her writing has appeared, among other places, in <em>Ms.</em>, <em>Penthouse</em>, <em>Chicago Sun-Times</em>, <em>On Our Backs</em>, and <em>Skeptical Inquirer</em>. She is editor of the "<em>Best Erotic Comics</em>" anthology series, and of "<em>Paying For It: A Guide by Sex Workers for Their Clients.</em>"</p>]]></description>
