<p>Stuart has a special interest in astronomy education, especially correcting myths and misconceptions about astronomy. To that end, he has a blog entitled&nbsp;<a href="http://pseudoastro.wordpress.com/" target="_blank">Exposing PseudoAstronomy</a>, and a&nbsp;<a href="http://podcast.sjrdesign.net/" target="_blank">podcast</a>&nbsp;by the same name. Since 2012 is supposed to be our last year on earth, again, Stuart dispels some claims about the Mayan Prophecy.</p>
