<p>Recently, we've seen a spate of news stories&mdash;and news incidents&mdash;involving conservative politicians and activists getting details wrong about American history.</p>
<p>There was, most infamously, Sarah Palin&nbsp;<a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oS4C7bvHv2w" target="_blank">saying that Paul Revere</a>, on his famous midnight ride, rang bells and "warned the British."</p>
