<p>And then was David Barton, conservatives' go-to guy on history,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.religiondispatches.org/dispatches/laurilebo/4736/david_barton:_creationist_founding_fathers_settled_debate_over_evolution/?comments=view&amp;cID=18746&amp;pID=18744" target="_blank">suggesting that Tom Paine</a>&nbsp;was, basically, a supporter of creationism.</p>
