            <description><![CDATA[<p>Andrew Mayne is a magician, paranormal illusionist, inventor, TV producer and skeptic.</p>
<p>One of the most creative and innovative minds in magic, Andrew has written and produced over 40 books and DVDs. Both creator and consultant, he has worked with a number of artists including David Blaine, and Penn &amp; Teller.</p>
<p>Andrew&rsquo;s performance material ranges from close-up and stage, to mentalism and illusion, and he is infamous for his brand of tricks, effects and stunts known as "shock magic". Far from pulling a rabbit out of a hat, Andrew&rsquo;s shock magic is described as "disturbing", "evil", "frightening" and "deadly".</p>
